Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}展开壮丽的"与彗星同行"之旅{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}on an epic journey to "Ride the Comet."{\r}
