Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去开始研究{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to catch our first glimpse of comets,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些自由任性 不肯与行星结合的石头堆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the wayward rocks that didn't meld into planets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}彗星其实是肮脏的雪球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Comets are basically dirty snowballs{\r}
