Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在冰块的作用下混合而成{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}held together by ices-{\r}
