Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}彗核也叫中央核心 它们的直径{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or central core, which averages in size{\r}
