Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}通过近距离观察{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One of the things we've learned{\r}
