Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们是奇怪的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is that they're these strange{\r}
