Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这种物质黑色无光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}this really dark, black material{\r}
