Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.37,0:42:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被发现的彗星超过 4 200颗{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}over 4,200 comets have been observed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.47,0:42:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但这只是这些冰团的一小部分{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a mere fraction of the total number of these icy bodies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.59,0:42:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这意味着数百万的未知彗星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This means billions of unknown comets{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.30,0:42:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还在外层空间潜伏着 等待着{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}still lie in wait in the outer reaches of space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.94,0:42:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}某一天 一颗末日彗星会被推出来{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One day, a doomsday comet could be nudged out{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.20,0:42:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}踏上与地球相撞的旅程{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and sent on a collision course with Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.26,0:42:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}假设我们是在宇宙里的高速公路上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If we're on that cosmic highway,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.15,0:42:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而它开进了我们的车道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and it's getting into our on-ramp,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.19,0:42:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们需要提防它{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we need to worry about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.41,0:43:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我们只有非常短的反应时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And we need to worry about it with very little lead time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.02,0:43:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们别无选择{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There is very little we can do,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.68,0:43:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只能向它们发射巨型原子弹{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}other than sending a giant bomb toward them{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.86,0:43:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}设法让它们转向{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and trying to deflect them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.24,0:43:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但非常棘手的是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But that's very difficult{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.73,0:43:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们只有几个月的预警时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when there's only a few months' warning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.37,0:43:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正如彗星让我们的祖先{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just as comets have inspired awe and fear{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.51,0:43:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}感到无比的敬畏和害怕{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}among our ancestors,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.23,0:43:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们今天依然不可藐视{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they remain a force to reckon with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.74,0:43:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}通过持续追踪它们的尘埃尾巴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}By continuing to track their tails of dust,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.18,0:43:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们也许能发现关于我们遥远过去的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we may uncover more clues about these frozen artifacts{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.43,0:43:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}更多线索{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of our ancient past.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.59,0:43:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你会觉得它很不寻常{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's pretty remarkable if you think about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.47,0:43:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在数百年前 我们不知道它们是什么{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just a few hundred years ago, we had no idea what they were.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.47,0:43:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知道它们的意义{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We had no idea what they meant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.98,0:43:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但现在我们已经去到了彗星表面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And now we've actually been to the surfaces of comets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.45,0:43:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}近距离地观察它们 去研究{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We've seen up close and personal what they're really like{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.26,0:43:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们的组成{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and what they're made out of.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.43,0:43:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}总之 这些神秘之物对人类{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So these mysterious objects have meant a lot to humans{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.15,0:43:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}意义非同凡响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}throughout our history.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.23,0:43:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们曾被视为异兆{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They've been agents of change.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.54,0:43:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们有时被当作灾星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They've been agents of destruction sometimes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.65,0:43:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们也许曾是造物使者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They've maybe been agents of creation.{\r}
